::Battera::

She was with Prime and another bot who were talking about Optimus 
Prime. She bowed to them and walked down the hall to her quaters.  
She stopped just outside her door and looked down.  This mission 
wsn't turning out so well. And now she had a wolverine bot how wanted 
to kill her despite her attemps at peace.  She sighed deeply.
